      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54 straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally pristine with documented subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings. Finished in original Carbon Black Metallic with zero paint correction required, this vehicle retains its factory-delivered mechanical tolerances and interior ergonomics, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak analog performance.",
